<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
    <title>【知識網】</title>
    <style>
        .btn{
            background: #f56c6c;
            display: inline-block;
            line-height: 1;
            white-space: nowrap;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid #f56c6c;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            outline: none;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: .1s;
            font-weight: 500;
            -moz-user-select: none;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -ms-user-select: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">
    <b>【知識網】最新一期香港《知識》雜誌電子版上線啦！</b><br><br>
    <p>親愛的 讀者，<span th:text="${nickName}"></span></p><br>
    <p>你好！新一期《知識》雜誌電子版（<span th:text="${releaseMonth}"></span>號）上線啦！</p><br>
    <p>一起來看看封面故事：</p><br><br>
    <p><img th:src="@{${coverUrl}}"/></p><br>
    <p>點擊下方按鈕或連結，開啟你的在線閱讀之旅！</p><br>
    <a th:href="@{${url}}"><button type="button" class="btn" >點擊閱讀</button></a><br><br>
    <p>最新一期《知識》雜誌（紙質版）<span th:text="${nextMonth}"></span>刊已出版，這期又有什麼精彩看點呢？歡迎前往香港便利店購買，或立即聯繫我們訂購吧！</p><br>
    <p>如有雜誌訂閱疑問，歡迎與我們聯繫。</p><br><br>
    <img src="https://upknowledge.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/content/20181218/logo20181218160451958.jpg" width="100" height="100" />
    <p>諮詢電話：2897 7200</p>
    <p>諮詢郵箱：upknowledge.school@gmail.com</p>
    <a th:href="@{${unsubUrl}}"><button type="button" class="btn" >取消訂閱</button></a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
